import React, { FC } from 'react' import { Food, Order } from '../type' import { useDispatch } from 'react-redux' import { OrderDelete } from '../store/menuSlice' interface ItemOrderType { product : Order } const ItemOrder:FC =({product}) => { const dispatch = useDispatch() const deleteItem = (id:number):void => { dispatch(OrderDelete(id)) } return (

{product.food_name}

{product.food_price}

) } export default ItemOrder
